ial contexts.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aDecolonizationxHistoriographyxAfrica. 0aDecolonizationxHistoriography. 0aDecolonizationzAfricaxHistoriography. 0aDécolonisationxHistoriographiexAfrique. 0aDécolonisationxHistoriographie. 0aImperialismxHistoriography. 0aImpérialismexHistoriographie. 7aHISTORY / World.2bisacsh  a20th century.  aafrica.  acivic.  acolonial contexts.  acolonial studies.  acolonial theory.  acolonialism.  acolonization.  adiaspora.  aessay collection.  aeurope.  aglobalization.  ahistorians.  ahistorical perspective.  ahistory of colonialism.  ahuman condition.  ahumanities.  aimperialism.  amodernity.  anational identity.  anationalism.  anonfiction essays.  apostcolonial.  aretrospective.  asocial sciences.  asouth asia.  atextbooks.  atheoretical.  awestern scholars.  aworld history.  aworld powers.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z978311069042240uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052093861840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520938618423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520938618/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles